TG = G4

for node in TG.nodes():
    ph_g = TG.copy()
    ph_g.remove_node(node)

    compare_g1 = rdd_iso.get_rdd_between_graphs_df_v2(ph_g)
    np_g1 = compare_g1.to_numpy()
    print(np_g1.sum())
